Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.43,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,Honey Heart Let's go party night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.60,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,心中的欢喜舞动无法克制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.01,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,难过的 快乐的 和你一起的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.34,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:31.89,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到真实的自己 很难变得成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:37.90,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在忘记了也没关系 夜阑静夜还会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:45.29,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,内心激动不已 相会之刻一起欢腾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:52.49,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在逐渐察觉 想要传达的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.81,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就算担忧着过去和未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.26,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不抱有希望就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:04.90,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,享受现在 It's all right！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.01,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:09.82,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的事全部都忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.86,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,和你携手步向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:19.73,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,可以成就更优秀的自己 有着这样的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.38,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不会结束的‘Ｇǒｌdｅｎ ☆ Τǐｍē’
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.52,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,和你逐渐缩短距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:33.59,OPEDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不离不弃 就算原地转圈 也想好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.43,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Honey Heart Let's go party night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心躍る  止められないの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.01,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,泣いて  笑って 君との記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:31.89,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,本当の自分はどこにいるとか  大人になるって大変で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:37.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,今は忘れてもいいかな  夜が待っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:45.29,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心を弾ませ  会える時は燥ぎまわれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:52.49,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,伝いたい想いに  いま  気づいてしまいそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.81,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,過去と未来  恐れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,空っぽのままじゃ動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:04.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しめば  It's all right！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.01,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,始めよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:09.82,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌なこと全部忘れて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君と一緒に踊り明かせば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:19.73,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと素敵な自分になれる そんなきがするの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.38,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,終わらない 『Ｇǒｌdｅｎ ☆ Τǐｍē』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.52,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キュッと近づく  君との距離は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:33.59,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,近ず離れず  回り道でも  大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达 好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达学姐和万里学长关系不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你们一定是在交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也太八卦了吧 是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是看护人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 万里很让人担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不能不管他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说喜欢万里学长 所以不能不管他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 我可没把他当男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙 我一点也不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:00:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊 万里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 万里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 万里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传球 传球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里 关于前些天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙 我一点也不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的都是反话啊 万里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时不时地会犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅犯傻的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不原谅 我也一点都不喜欢琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时 我的心被点亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达说一点也不喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这句话跟她的真心是相反的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:04.89,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(626,524)}Reset
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许琳达她...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？柳兄他早退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 所以多田你能去光央住的地方看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道 我是一定不能去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都有男朋友了 怎么可能去别的男生家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟异性在房间里独处 这可是出轨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也...也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回隔壁去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多田 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在听 在听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我会去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法忘记对琳达的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,82)}知道了 待会联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使现在成了幽灵...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,76)}那先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这与现在的多田万里无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.50,ext,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,234)\frz0.407}笨蛋琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.50,ext2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,492)}傻蛋万里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在的万里在和加贺香子在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个... 是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我身体不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以逞强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给你做个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳你喜欢吃土豆炖肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一直有空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我今晚在这里过夜也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 骗人吧 不要吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hi~柳兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？这是啥米？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Boyfriend ！啾~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的男朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间是容不下第三者的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们前世是恋人啦 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 前世我是牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是修道院的修女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得...得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是影研的玲奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓死我了 她秀了很深的乳沟给我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是垃圾堆填区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 特意让你赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从加贺那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又和小冈发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小柳 今天可不会让你逃掉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千波 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些抱歉 但你能不能不要和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为前段时间聚会的事 很多人都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是一直不要和你说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然小柳你这样说的话 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...hi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你擅自走到我旁边的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是前阵子在聚会向千波表白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后秒速被甩的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人心痛啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳兄？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉...周围的人都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被千波甩了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道之后我做什么都在意别人的眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该像什么都没发现那样平常的接触千波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 一见到面又会‘哇’的紧张起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又尴尬 又难过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳兄 你好好看看你现在这张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牙齿上粘着海苔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我吃了便利店的寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是你是一个帅哥 应该自信一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之你这样下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我被琳达学姐救助那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次让我来帮你想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达学姐帮你什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 二次元君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 现在我想开一个‘柳兄鼓励派对’
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 多田你迟到了15分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的 我才没有生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能见到多田 我 很 高 兴 哦 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能见到柳兄 我 很 高 兴 哦 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...一点都不高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不能这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 虽然我很感谢大家为我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可没有预料到这家伙也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我接到万里电话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好和加贺同学一起上完课 被她听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想一直和多田在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光央的事我一点也不在乎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来游乐场是我的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是觉得不爽的话你大可以回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你在只会碍事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,74)}加贺...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 是小冈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要接啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳兄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我哦 我们接下来要开‘柳兄鼓励派对’
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是不想你来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为了光央 还是万分不情愿的叫你来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,76)}喂喂 是这么回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又为了光央用了我的温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要补给~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(656,72)}你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你所听的那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是回去？还是留下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 小冈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们现在在检票处等你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来游乐场的话 我还是想和多田两人来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 下次我们两个人一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上泳池就要开发了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说干脆直接去海边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我要和多田一起去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺同学也来接我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才的电话我还真的吓一跳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺突然接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有惊讶完 她就叫我马上过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得必须得过去 我犹豫带什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 我就带了这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 这确实要犹豫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 万里和加贺同学正在交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次听二次元君说了 而且又看到你们牵手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我根本不想你来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让你进入我的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...不是加贺叫人过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为光央受伤了 我只是稍微同情一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且他是我的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且让你们见面也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请不要让光央更难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果办不到的话 请马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说这些话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和加贺同学都没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小柳之间发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和加贺同学你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺同学不是和万里在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更珍惜现在手中所拥有的东西怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把面还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没...没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没有坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是能拍到...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是加贺同学 加贺香子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第一次用‘冈相机’拍摄你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 加贺同学 其实我也是很难受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 因为 小柳...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了再也不要和我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！只有我才能在多田面前卖萌撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要忍住 忍住！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你哭完之前我都会一直这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺  小冈这样会窒息的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得你要哭完了 就给我暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就会一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 小冈会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还...还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 万里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在是不是超有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 要拍吗 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺同学 能不能放开手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在情绪感觉很平静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我放了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那么我们先坐什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是尖叫系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像他们和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多田你的眼里只能有我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个是颜脸炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜脸炒面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃吗 柳兄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,78)}请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,80)}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我们要不要来个协定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协定？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像今天一样有游玩或聚会大家都尽量出席
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做的话不就能聚到几个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多田要加入的话我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不喜欢和光央一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.21,Warn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz15.929\pos(434.857,517.714)}To：琳达学姐 还没睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达...学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有现在 我能哀叹一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这样可以轻松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在NANA学姐的房间里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正好想起你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一收到你的简讯真吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么知道我还醒着？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 就有那种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里以前也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像社团活动的合宿要出远门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜睡不着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会潜入女生的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后问‘喂 琳达还醒着吗’
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这不是色狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也觉得很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你摆着一副超级郁闷的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说着‘我睡不着 明天的练习惨了’之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那行动绝对有色色企图
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我的内裤不见了 实际上是万里...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢 我总有这样一种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那时候自己喜欢着琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以刚才也是借失眠的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想看看琳达睡觉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点下流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此...抱歉 我先道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初就像这样 自然地聊着往事该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些话一旦没有说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就会越来越难开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事都直率地说出来 那才是最佳选择
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和万里之间已经没有秘密了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人像这样好好地活着 仰望同一片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与过去一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实有件事一直没问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业典礼的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于告白 你的回答是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还要问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答当然是NO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是无法将万里当做恋爱对象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算回复我们从此以后一直是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达...学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回到那个时候吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方 有我存在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...刚才...说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 刚才的一瞬间你竟然直接睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你该休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眠不足对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神经也綳直了 会考虑些不切实际的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 多田万里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到现在 我依然喜欢着琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话 我想一直待在琳达的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却无法与你分离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就有这样一种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
